text="Aspects of predicative algebraic set theory III: sheaves">Aspects of predicative algebraic set theory III: sheaves</fr:title><fr:taxon>Reference</fr:taxon><fr:date><fr:year>2012</fr:year></fr:date><fr:authors><fr:author><fr:link
